Class DailyStockData

  • java.lang.Object
    • stocks.DailyStockData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StockData
    public class DailyStockData
extends java.lang.Object
implements StockData
    The stocks.DailyStockData class represents day-to-day stock data in the form of high, low, open, close, and volume values.
